videos.headline: Colby Jones makes nice move for reverse lay-in
videos.description: Colby Jones does a great job to get to the basket to knock down a reverse lay-in for Xavier.

videos.headline: Xavier hands UConn its first loss of the season
videos.description: No. 22 Xavier upsets No. 2 UConn 83-73 to hand the Huskies their first loss of the season.
